data.description: Stunning & Spacious 2 Story home with all the luxury upgrades will have you saying, ''This is the One!'' Right at first glance, the beautiful landscaping will have your jaw dropping! Entering this meticulously clean home, you will see upgrades at every turn. The kitchen has plenty of cabinets & counter-top space w/ new granite & backsplash. Large living room has new gas fireplace w/ custom stonework. Formal dining room, 1st floor office/den & 1st flr laundry rm. Walk out the new sliding door to see your inground saltwater pool! Fenced in backyard is perfect for entertaining! The 2nd flr has large bedrooms, including the primary  en suite that includes his closet & the dream walk-in closet for her! Full basement that can easily be finished! 2+ car garage has workshop & loft storage space
